18 § 254. OFFICE OF HEALTH EQUITY
19 (a) There is established the Office of Health Equity within the Department
20 of Health for the purpose of eliminating avoidable and unjust disparities in
21 health among Vermonters. The Office shall use a systemic and comprehensive
